//         "\begin{?}>"
//      and / or
//         "$$>"
//      and / or
//         "\[>"
//      and maybe also "\end{?}>" etc.
//    * Define the Action:
//          Exe("%B\Macros\LaTeX\ChangeEnvMUI.edt");
//    * Check the box in "Action" and define "TeX" as "On Type".
//
